      "Advantages": "[{\"MainHeader\":\"Advantages\",\"SubTitleText\":\"The nanoScan3 advances the miniaturization of high-precision and extremely rugged safety laser scanners. Thanks to the low height of 80\\u00a0mm, even small automated guided vehicles (AGVs) can be very well equipped \\u2013 and production and logistics can be automated in more versatile ways.\",\"RightVideo\":{\"ID\":null},\"CenterVideo\":{\"ID\":null},\"Sequence\":60,\"HeaderImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/2/42/542/IM0086542.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0086542_en\"},\"LeftText\":\"Low space requirements: The nanoScan3 was specially developed for small automated guided vehicles.\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"Header\":\"Space-saving safety solution for AGVs and AGCs\",\"LeftVideo\":{\"ID\":null},\"Headline\":\"\",\"LeftImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/5/45/545/IM0086545.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0086545_en\"},\"ID\":\"advantage_p676199_en\",\"CenterImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"RightImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"SubTitle\":\"The smallest safety laser scanner from SICK \\u2013 extremely rugged and highly precise\"},{\"RightText\":\"The precise measurement data of the nanoScan3 is very well suited for vehicle localization.\",\"SubTitleText\":\"<p>Dirt, dust, and ambient light are all par for the course in rough industrial environments. With this in mind, it is reassuring to know that the nanoScan3 can withstand these ambient conditions. This is partly thanks to the patented scanning technology safeHDDM<sup>\\u00ae</sup>. It uses numerous laser pulses to accurately detect its environment \\u2013 with a scanning angle of 275\\u00b0.</p><p><a href=\\\"https://www.sick.com/safehddm\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Find out more</a></p>\",\"RightVideo\":{\"Title\":\"Precise measurement data with safeHDDM<sup>\\u00ae</sup> battles single-puls scanning technology\",\"Type\":\"video\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"ID\":\"vQ5NmVj0dzM\"},\"CenterVideo\":{\"Title\":\"nanoScan3 from SICK proves its robustness\",\"Type\":\"video\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"ID\":\"XLhmk5L5ebI\"},\"Sequence\":70,\"HeaderImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/9/29/529/IM0086529.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0086529_en\"},\"LeftText\":\"safeHDDM<sup>\\u00ae</sup> makes safety laser scanners such as the nanoScan3 from SICK very resistant and reliable.\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"Header\":\"safeHDDM<sup>\\u00ae</sup> ensures high machine productivity\",\"CenterText\":\"Remains undisturbed while at work: the nanoScan3 is resistant to dirt, dust and ambient light.\",\"LeftVideo\":{\"Title\":\"safeHDDM\\u00ae from SICK: Innovative scanning technology explained\",\"Type\":\"video\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"ID\":\"mEQoy0ptyy4\"},\"Headline\":\"\",\"LeftImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"ID\":\"advantage_p676200_en\",\"CenterImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"RightImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"SubTitle\":\"Reliable accuracy thanks to safeHDDM<sup>\\u00ae</sup> scanning technology                          \"},{\"SubTitleText\":\"With the versatile Safety Designer\\u00a0software, configuration and commissioning of the nanoScan3 is quick and easy. You can easily implement and use safety functions in the safety laser scanner. Detailed diagnostic information about the device can also be easily retrieved.\",\"RightVideo\":{\"ID\":null},\"CenterVideo\":{\"Title\":\"nanoScan3: Individual field settings using the Safety Designer\",\"Type\":\"video\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"ID\":\"i_s3VMbyiq0\"},\"Sequence\":80,\"HeaderImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/2/32/532/IM0086532.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0086532_en\"},\"LeftText\":\"128\\u00a0monitoring cases can be implemented according to the application and enable fluid movements and flexible routes from mobile platforms.\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"Header\":\"Save resources and prevent unplanned machine downtime\",\"CenterText\":\"Individual field settings enable the adjustment of vehicle movements to the current hazard level.\",\"LeftVideo\":{\"Title\":\"nanoScan3: Field configuration with the Safety Designer\",\"Type\":\"video\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"ID\":\"gf2r4SeSqPg\"},\"Headline\":\"\",\"LeftImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"ID\":\"advantage_p676201_en\",\"CenterImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"RightImage\":{\"URL\":null},\"SubTitle\":\"Intuitive configuration, commissioning and diagnostics with Safety Designer\"},{\"RightText\":\"High productivity thanks to central diagnostics via Safety\\u00a0Designer and safe integration into industrial networks, e.g. EtherNet/IP\\u2122\\u00a0CIP\\u00a0Safety\\u2122, I/O or the intelligent Safe\\u00a0EFI-pro\\u00a0system.\",\"SubTitleText\":\"Thanks to standardized interfaces, cabling costs for the safety laser scanner are low. And it can be easily integrated into machines with its inputs and outputs. In addition, a configuration memory integrated in the system plug enables quick device replacement.\",\"RightVideo\":{\"ID\":null},\"CenterVideo\":{\"ID\":null},\"Sequence\":90,\"HeaderImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/6/36/536/IM0086536.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0086536_en\"},\"LeftText\":\"<p>Important diagnostic data can be viewed using the display and highly-visible LEDs or read out using the Safety\\u00a0Designer software.</p><p/>\",\"Language\":\"en\",\"Header\":\"Simple machine integration and quick device replacement\",\"CenterText\":\"Quick device replacement without new cabling and configuration thanks to the removable system plug with integrated configuration memory.\",\"LeftVideo\":{\"ID\":null},\"Headline\":\"\",\"LeftImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/7/27/527/IM0086527.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0086527_en\"},\"ID\":\"advantage_p676202_en\",\"CenterImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/6/26/526/IM0086526.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0086526_en\"},\"RightImage\":{\"URL\":\"https://cdn.sick.com/media/pim/4/84/284/IM0105284.jpg\",\"Type\":\"image_variant\",\"ID\":\"im0105284_en\"},\"SubTitle\":\"Smart integration via standard interfaces\"}]",
